query:
SELECT c.nome, DATE_FORMAT(f.dataFesta, '%d/%m/%Y') as data_br, DATE_FORMAT(f.dataFesta, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') as data_completa
FROM festas f
JOIN clientes c ON f.clienteId = c.id
WHERE c.nome LIKE '%Rodrigo%'
LIMIT 1
